        "created_at": "2021-01-23T00:24:21.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=3487023\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>2018 Domaine Michel Niellon Chassagne-Montrachet 1er Cru Les Chaum\u00e9es Clos de la Truffi\u00e8re</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Chassagne-Montrachet 1er Cru (1/22/2021)</em><br>\nGorgeous nose with aeration. Bright golden fruit. Vibrant. Beautiful palate with golden fruit, minerals and a mid palate presence that is full and glorious. The finish is loaded with mineral notes. Long finish. Extremely elegant. The balance here is very special. This is so nice and will improve for sure. Nice job by the wonderful female winemaker, Michel Coutoux\u2019s daughter.BTW, William Kelley nailed this one.  His take is perfect.  Check it out.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
